Foodalytics

Managing Food Inventories

Foodalytics brings the power of computer vision to your kitchen, helping you manage your food inventories without you having to lift a finger.

Learn More

Managing Your Food Inventory:

Waste Less, Save money

Quickly View The Things That Matter

From the home page, see a snapshot of your inventory history and gain insights into how to waste less and become more profitable.

View and Manage Your Inventory

View the food that's currently on your shelves and in your fridge, as well as information about when it will expire.

Easily See Trends in Your History

Quickly view visualizations of your inventory's history, including statistics about your profits, food waste, and food quantity distributions.

Stay Informed

Receive notifications about food items you're running low on, food that is about to expire, and daily, weekly, monthly, and yearly profit trends.

Features

Update System Seamlessly

Uses Computer Vision to record when items are added or removed from inventory and updates the system automatically

View and Manage Inventory

View and manage what's on your shelves in the system

View Statistics and Insights

Quickly view graphs and statistics of your inventory's history and trends over time and receive suggestions on how to reduce waste and save money

Get Notifications

Receive notifications when food is about to expire or is running low
